      <p><strong>Malasana</strong> is the sweet spot for most tourists. It has the highest concentration of tourist-friendly clubs, is well-connected by metro (Tribunal, Noviciado), and has a vibrant nightlife scene that pairs well with club visits. The scam risk is moderate because of the tourist foot traffic, but if you have a verified invitation you can bypass the street approaches entirely.</p>

